{"tid":2446409,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★美國派錢市民如何使用？調查：35%還債，20%購買生活必需品，20%用作儲蓄","createTime":"2021-03-14T12:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T18:49:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1e0c2588f58ddb48492575429fcdb2a9b289aa","tid":2446409,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"該調查訪問3,558名美國居民，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>35%受訪者會將政府派發的紓困資金用作償還債務或繳付帳單；20%表示會用作儲蓄；20%用於購買生活必需品；5%會購入自己的頭好；3%會用作捐款</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國國家稅務局（IRS）聲明表示，第一輪款項以電子轉帳形式發放，除部分補助家庭在周末會收到匯款外，大部分人將在下周收到。未來數周內，將陸續透過電子轉帳、郵寄支票、簽帳金融卡方式發送其他批次的紓困金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/599140/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-35-%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E8%80%85%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E9%82%84%E5%82%B5-%E5%83%855-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F599140%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A6%2582%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-35-%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25BD%259C%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%2582%25B5-%25E5%2583%25855-%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%25B8%2582&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfHqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=9bc635a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/599140/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-35-%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E8%80%85%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%9C%E9%82%84%E5%82%B5-%E5%83%855-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82</a>"},{"pid":"1679115564c4985f8884d86c1b979b6193512963","tid":2446409,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"